<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:#FF0000;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; **</span><a href="http://www.tsunami.gov/"><span style="color:#FF0000;">Get Tsunami Alerts</span></a><span style="color:#FF0000;">**</span></strong></p>

<div style=" border-top-left-radius:10px; width: 250px; background: #1a2757; padding-bottom: 6px;
    padding-top: 6px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid white;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span style="color:#FFFFFF;">Tsunami Safety Resources</span></strong></span></div>

<div id="id01">&nbsp;</div>
